<br>
Think about the experiences Huck has had after leaving Hannibal. Identify the single experience you think affected Huck the most. In other words, what happened that changed Huck the most in your opinion. Identify your answer and explain in a complete paragraph why you think this the most significant event in the novel. <br>
<br>
